evidence.text: Clerks Notice of Judge Assignment to Judge Jose E. Martinez. Pursuant to 28 USC 636(c), the parties are hereby notified that the U.S. Magistrate Judge Eduardo I. Sanchez is available to handle any or all proceedings in this case.
Magistrate Judge Eduardo I. Sanchez no longer referred on the case.
4 The case was originally assigned to Judge Jose Martinez, (DE 2), but was reassigned to this Court on July 16, 2025. (DE 37).
Signed by Judge Kathleen M. Williams on 7/18/2025.
